# Multi-Modal Deepfake Defense Gateway: Phase 1 - Blink Detection

This phase focuses on building the **Vision Engine's core component**: the real-time Blink Detector. It uses the Eye Aspect Ratio (EAR) metric to analyze the physical integrity of a user's biological behavior.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This script requires a working webcam and will request access to it.
> Since it uses `mediapipe`, the first run might take a few seconds to initialize the AI models.

## Proposed Changes

### [Core Engine]

#### [NEW] [blink_detector.py](file:///C:/Users/HP%20USER/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/deepfake_defense_gateway/blink_detector.py)
A Python script that:
- Initializes the webcam stream.
- Loads MediaPipe Face Mesh for real-time 3D landmark tracking.
