## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `python blink_detector.py` and verify that the webcam opens.
- Observe the "EAR" graph and verify it drops when eyes are closed.
- Verify that the blink counter increments correctly.

### Manual Verification
- Test natural blinking vs. forced slow blinking to see how the system logs the behavior.
- Use a photo of a face (which doesn't blink) to ensure the system remains at zero blinks and identifies "No Biological Activity Detected".
